"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    This patients exhibits features of severe&nbsp;venous insufficiency combined with lymphedema. Chronic venous insufficiency may result in lipodermatosclerosis, a fibrosing panniculitis characterized by advanced hyperpigmentation and induration, in this case&nbsp;involving most of the leg circumferentially.",
